a%20producer%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20trying%20to%20take%20care%20of%20them%20because%20if%20they're%20not%20happy%2C%20they%20could%20pull%20the%20rug.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20hard%20was%20it%20to%20convince%20Streep%2C%20by%20then%20a%20two-time%20Oscar%20winner%2C%20to%20come%20on%20board%3F%20After%20she%20plucked%20up%20the%20courage%20to%20ask%20her%2C%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bsurprisingly%20easy%26quot%3B%20Craymer%20responded.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EStreep%20had%20just%20appeared%20in%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-devil-wears-prada-director-david-frankel-interview-film-secrets-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Devil%20Wears%20Prada%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20Craymer%20says%20she%20and%20Lloyd%20really%20wanted%20her%20to%20play%20Donna%20in%20the%20film%20after%20seeing%20her%20singing%20and%20pulling%20a%20wagon%20in%20a%20production%20of%20%3Cspan%3EBertolt%20Brecht's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3BMother%20Courage%20and%20her%20Children%26quot%3B%20in%20New%20York.%20After%20breaking%20with%20convention%20by%20calling%20Streep's%20agent%20directly%2C%20the%20pair%20met%20with%20the%20actor%20for%20coffee.%20%26quot%3BSo%20do%20you%20want%20me%3F%26quot%3B%20Streep%20asked%20them%2C%20Craymer%20recalls%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20squealed%20a%20lot%26quot%3B%20after%20her%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Director%20Phyllida%20Lloyd%2C%20Ashley%20Lilley%2C%20Judy%20Craymer%2C%20Colin%20Firth%2C%20Meryl%20Streep%2C%20Pierce%20Brosnan%2C%20Amanda%20Seyfried%2C%20Colin%20Firth%2C%20Julie%20Walters%20and%20Dominic%20Cooper%20at%20the%20London%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BMamma%20Mia%26quot%3B%20in%20June%202008.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669925b949138fa6f6e36682%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222218%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDirector%20Phyllida%20Lloyd%2C%20Ashley%20Lilley%2C%20Judy%20Craymer%2C%20Colin%20Firth%2C%20Meryl%20Streep%2C%20Pierce%20Brosnan%2C%20Amanda%20Seyfried%2C%20Stellan%20Skarsg%C3%A5rd%2C%20Julie%20Walters%20and%20Dominic%20Cooper%20at%20the%20London%20premiere%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BMamma%20Mia!%26quot%3B%20movie%20in%20June%202008.%3Cp%3EDave%20M.%20Benett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20film's%20huge%20success%20meant%20a%20sequel%20was%20always%20on%20the%20cards%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmamma-mia-here-we-go-again-movie-review-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMamma%20Mia!%20Here%20We%20Go%20Again%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20followed%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20adding%20Cher%20to%20the%20cast%20(playing%20Donna's%20mother)%20and%20taking%20around%20%24400%20million%20on%20a%20budget%20of%20%2475%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20Cher%2C%20Craymer%20sips%20on%20an%20Aqua%20de%20Madre%20pink%20grapefruit%20and%20lime%20water%20kefir%20while%20we%20speak%20in%20her%20central%20London%20office%2C%20which%20is%20filled%20with%20%26quot%3BMamma%20Mia!%26quot%3B%20promotional%20items%20and%20pictures.%20She%20says%20Cher%20put%20her%20on%20to%20the%20drink%20while%20shooting%20the%20sequel%20(I%20had%20one%20too%2C%20and%20it's%20very%20refreshing%20indeed).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Cher%20biopic%20is%20in%20the%20works%2C%20with%20a%20script%20written%20but%20casting%20yet%20to%20be%20revealed.%20Craymer%20says%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20life%26quot%3B%20to%20try%20to%20fit%20into%20110%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cher%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BMamma%20Mia!%20Here%20We%20Go%20Again%26quot%3B%20world%20premiere%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6696457b9caa6ed01e01e607%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222409%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECher%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BMamma%20Mia!%20Here%20We%20Go%20Again%26quot%3B%20premiere%20in%20London%20in%20July%202018.%3Cp%3EWiktor%20Szymanowicz%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20project%20also%20in%20the%20works%20is%20a%20third%20%26quot%3BMamma%20Mia!%26quot%3B%20film%2C%20which%20she%20thinks%20could%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Bevent%20movie%26quot%3B%20given%20its%20broad%20appeal.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20stars%20are%20aligned%20%E2%80%94%20I%20really%20want%20there%20to%20be%20another%20one.%20It's%20something%20in%20my%20sights%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECraymer%2C%2066%2C%20says%20the%20cast%20are%20always%20being%20asked%20about%20another%20%26quot%3BMamma%20Mia!%26quot%3B%20no%20matter%20what%20project%20they're%20promoting.%20%26quot%3BMeryl%20was%20saying%20in%20Cannes%20'oh%20yeah%20there%20will%20be%20another%20one'%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20Pierce%20is%20on%20the%20phone%20going%20%26quot%3Bwhat's%20she%20saying%3F'%26quot%3B%20before%20laughing%20loudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20wonder%20if%20there%20are%20enough%20Abba%20songs%20left%20for%20another%20film%2C%20but%20the%20group%20helpfully%20released%20a%20new%20album%20in%20late%202021%20(their%20first%20new%20music%20in%2040%20years)%20that%20contains%20a%20couple%20of%20tracks%20you%20could%20imagine%20being%20used%20(%26quot%3BI%20Still%20Have%20Faith%20In%20You%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDon't%20Shut%20Me%20Down.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20songs%20also%20appear%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabba-voyage-london-future-of-live-entertainment-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAbba%20Voyage%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bconcert%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20been%20playing%20in%20a%20purpose-built%20venue%20in%20London%20for%20just%20over%20two%20years.%20It%20uses%20breathtakingly%20effective%20technology%2C%20along%20with%20a%20live%20band%2C%20that%20makes%20you%20almost%20believe%20the%20four%20members%20of%20Abba%20are%20up%20there%20on%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ABBA%20Voyage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64fa439da39a1b00190b45b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223344%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAbba%20Voyage%20has%20been%20playing%20in%20London%20since%20May%202022.%3Cp%3EABBA%20Voyage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Craymer%20says%20Abba%20Voyage%20is%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20entertainment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20thinks%20AI%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20creative%20industries%20that%20require%20stronger%20copyright%20laws%20to%20protect%20artists'%20likenesses%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20to%20be%20controlled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20and%20the%20Hollywood%20strikes%20were%20a%20double%20whammy%20for%20the%20entertainment%20industry%2C%20but%20she's%20hopeful%20that%20seeing%20a%20live%20performance%20remains%20compelling%20for%20audiences%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20download%20theatre%2C%20you%20can't%20AI%20theatre%20%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECraymer%20says%20the%20%26quot%3BMamma%20Mia!%26quot%3B%20movies%20continue%20to%20drive%20particularly%20younger%20audiences%20to%20see%20the%20musical%20(the%20UK%20and%20international%20tour%20hits%20the%2020-year%20mark%20in%20September%2C%20while%20another%20is%20playing%20in%20North%20America).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225fc314f6-c5db-4d1c-98a9-4e8b0e7b4668%5C%22%3E'Incredibly%20exciting'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHad%20she%20listened%20to%20her%20father%2C%20Craymer%20might%20have%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20lawyer%20like%20him.%20However%2C%20in%201977%2C%20she%20heard%20about%20the%20stage%20management%20course%20at%20London's%20Guildhall%20School%20of%20Drama%2C%20decided%20to%20apply%2C%20and%20got%20accepted.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20great%20entry%20into%20messing%20about%20backstage%20and%20learning%20the%20craft%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20incredibly%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20started%20as%20a%20stage%20manager%20I%20always%20liked%20hanging%20out%20with%20the%20actors%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20never%20wanted%20to%20be%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20career%20saw%20her%20work%20with%20Cameron%20Mackintosh%20and%20Andrew%20Lloyd%20Webber%2C%20and%20she%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20original%20West%20End%20production%20of%20%26quot%3BCats%26quot%3B%20in%201981.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222882%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrew%20Lloyd-Webber%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5df96221acb8fb3f7d5d0b99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222112%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrew%20Lloyd%20Webber%20with%20a%20cast%20of%20%26quot%3BCats%26quot%3B%20in%201985.%3Cp%3EBruce%20Milton%20Miller%2FFairfax%20Media%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20certainly%20don't%20go%20into%20theatre%20to%20make%20money%2C%20or%20any%20of%20the%20creative%20industries.%20You%20need%20to%20love%20it.%20And%20if%20you%20do%20make%20money%20and%20you%20can%20pay%20the%20rent%20that's%20fantastic.%26quot%3B%20Craymer%20recalls%20once%20trying%20to%20explain%20to%20a%20potential%20investor%20that%20they%20might%20not%20get%20their%20money%20back%20if%20the%20show%20wasn't%20a%20success%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20was%20going%20to%20be%20kneecapped.%20It's%20tough%20doing%20theatre%20-%20it's%20such%20a%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20running%20Littlestar%20Services%2C%20the%20company%20set%20up%20in%201996%20with%20Andersson%2C%20Ulvaeus%2C%20and%20Richard%20East%20to%20produce%20the%20%26quot%3BMamma%20Mia!%26quot%3B%20musical%2C%20Craymer%20had%20a%20stint%20as%20chair%20of%20Universal%20Music%20that%20spanned%20its%20stock%20market%20debut%20in%20September%202021.%20(You%20may%20have%20guessed%20that%20Abba%20is%20on%20Universal%20Music.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222403%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Lucian%20Grainge%20of%20Universal%20Music%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669a7ddafb2b6bedb058af6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221802%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaylor%20Swift%20and%20Lucian%20Grainge%20at%20the%202016%20Grammy%20Awards.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Buckner%2FVariety%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20asked%20by%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-music-ceo-gets-new-contract-with-100m-stock-options-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELucian%20Grainge%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20chair%20the%20board%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20honor%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20probably%20chosen%20because%20I%20was%20good%20with%20personalities%20%E2%80%94%20I%20understand%20the%20artists%2C%20and%20I%20understand%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECraymer's%20role%20sometimes%20involves%20dealing%20with%20requests%20from%20the%20talent%20%E2%80%94%20or%20the%20co-owners.%20Earlier%20on%20the%20day%20we%20met%20she%20recalls%20a%20request%20from%20Ulvaeus%20that%20crossed%20her%20desk.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20show%20the%20movie%20under%20the%20stars%20in%20Sweden%2C%26quot%3B%20Craymer%20says%20he%20asked.%20She%20called%20him%20back%20and%20said%20%26quot%3BOK%2C%20we'll%20allow%20that%20%E2%80%A6%20just%20checking%20it%20was%20you.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmamma-mia-musical-judy-craymer-abba-meryl-streep-london-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722164642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66991d8e80d4d5da13d4e287%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmamma-mia-musical-judy-craymer-abba-meryl-streep-london-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judy%20Craymer%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20Abba%20songs%20in%20a%20musical.%2