el%20alloy%20wheel%20at%20the%20right%20front%20corner%20of%20a%202024%20Genesis%20GV60%20EV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3fbfcaab37011780afd57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222615%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%2021-inch%20wheels%20on%20the%20GV60%20Performance.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GV60%20Standard%20comes%20with%2019-inch%20wheels%2C%20while%20the%20Advanced%20trim%20gets%2020-inch%20units.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInside%2C%20the%20GV60%20is%20pure%20class.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20dash%20of%20a%202024%20Genesis%20GV60%20EV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3d8cea0fc5856d597d27c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20GV60's%20front%20dash.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGenesis%20went%20all%20out%20with%20the%20design%20of%20the%20GV60's%20cabin%2C%20with%20a%20delightful%20blend%20of%20materials%20and%20textures%20from%20aluminum%20trim%20pieces%20to%20the%20microfiber%20suede%20headliner%20and%20quilted%20Nappa%20Leather%20seats.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20GV60's%20dash%20is%20dominated%20by%20a%2012.3%20inch%20infotainment%20display.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%2012.3-inch%20infotainment%20screen%20on%20the%20front%20dash%20of%20a%202024%20Genesis%20GV60%20EV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3d73ca0fc5856d597cf92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20GV60's%2012.3-inch%20infotainment%20screen.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20screen%20is%20home%20to%20the%20GV60's%20infotainment%20system%2C%20which%20looks%20great%20and%20is%20a%20breeze%20to%20navigate.%20The%20system%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20host%20of%20interesting%20features%2C%20such%20as%20quiet%20mode%2C%20which%20mutes%20rear%20cabin%20speakers%20to%20allow%20passengers%20to%20relax%20in%20peace%2C%20and%20a%20built-in%20diagnostic%20system%20that%20allows%20owners%20to%20check%20the%20operating%20condition%20of%20the%20vehicle's%20various%20functions.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20screen%20is%20also%20home%20to%20the%20GV60's%20surround%20view%20camera.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20360-degree%20surrounding%20view%20is%20generated%20by%20the%20cameras%20of%20a%202024%20GV60%20EV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3cc3caab37011780add97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20GV60's%20360-degree%20surround%20view%20camera.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20feature%20stitches%20together%20images%20from%20the%20handful%20of%20cameras%20around%20the%20car%20to%20create%20a%20360-degree%20views%20of%20its%20surroundings.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUnder%20the%20infotainment%20screen%20is%20a%20smaller%20climate-control%20screen.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20climate%20control%20display%20on%20the%20front%20dash%20of%20a%202024%20Genesis%20GV60%20EV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3d93eaab37011780aeb03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20GV60's%20climate%20control%20display.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20touchscreen%20and%20accompanying%20physical%20buttons%20made%20controlling%20the%20GV60's%20HVAC%20functions%20an%20easy%20task.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20front%20of%20the%20driver%20are%20a%20heated%20steering%20wheel%20and%20digital%20gauge%20cl