3Cp%3EWe've%20moved%20not%20knowing%20if%20it%20will%20be%20two%20months%20or%20five%20years%20%E2%80%94%20we've%20probably%20spent%20several%20years%20living%20out%20of%20a%20suitcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20times%20when%20it's%20a%20bit%20lean%20and%20times%20when%20it's%20not.%20There's%20definitely%20a%20sacrifice%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20when%20the%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20started%2C%20I%20moved%20my%20family%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20stage%2C%20I%20spent%2010%20weeks%20doing%20medevac%20for%20the%20Ukrainian%20armed%20forces.%20That%20was%20high%20intensity%20%E2%80%94%20my%20colleagues%20and%20I%20got%20targeted%20and%20shelled%20so%20many%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b72dbc6-fccf-461e-ade3-6ef130b08be2%5C%22%3ELearning%20to%20handle%20fear%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20time%2C%20in%20the%20winter%20of%202022%2C%20we%20were%20distributing%20supplies%20in%20a%20frontline%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20four%20vehicles%20in%20there%2C%20about%20seven%20people.%20I%20had%20scattered%20and%20hidden%20our%20vehicles%20so%20that%20if%20we%20do%20get%20bombed%2C%20we're%20not%20in%20one%20big%20pile.%20But%20then%20one%20of%20the%20guys%20got%20on%20the%20radio%20and%20said%20a%20rocket%20had%20landed%20about%2030%20yards%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%20there%20were%20rockets%20landing%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20very%20religious%2C%20and%20I'd%20always%20thought%20that%20God%20would%20take%20care%20of%20us.%20But%20now%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20God%20would%20come%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20about%2020%20seconds%20to%20recalibrate%20myself%20and%20deal%20with%20it.%20It%20didn't%20last%20very%20long%2C%20but%20I%20barely%20dealt%20with%20fear%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20shelled%20so%20many%20times%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20I%20got%20comfortable%20knowing%20they're%20trying%20to%20kill%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt