20to%20go%20out%20of%20Maharashtra.%20He%20also%20asked%20me%20to%20not%20reveal%20it%20to%20anyone...I%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%20since%20I%20was%2012-13%20and%20completed%20its%20three-year%20course.%20Till%201980%20I%20was%20with%20the%20Jana%20Sangh.%20I%20like%20taking%20up%20challenges.%20I%20may%20have%20been%20chosen%20for%20this%20post%20because%20of%20my%20work%20in%20the%20party%20for%20so%20may%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20facts%20about%20Haribhau%20Bagde%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHaribhau%20Bagde%2C%20fondly%20called%20Nana%20by%20his%20supporters%2C%20was%20born%20on%20August%2017%2C%201945%2C%20in%20Phulamri%20taluka%20of%20then%20Aurangabad%20(Chhatrapati%20Sambhaji%20Nagar).%20He%20was%20born%20into%20a%20poor%20farmer%20family.%20Mr%20Bagde%20sold%20newspapers%20for%20many%20years.%20He%20could%20attend%20school%20only%20up%20to%20Class%2010.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%2078-year-old%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%20since%20his%20teenage%20years.%20The%20BJP%20gave%20him%20a%20ticket%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%201985%2C%20and%20he%20was%20elected%20as%20an%20MLA%20from%20the%20Aurangabad%20East%20seat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20coalition%20came%20to%20power%20in%201995%2C%20Haribhau%20Bagde%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20Minister%20for%20the%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20five-time%20MLA%2C%20he%20won%20the%202014%20Assembly%20elections%20against%20Kalyan%20Kale%20of%20the%20Congress%20from%20Phulambri.%20He%20again%20won%20the%202019%20elections%20from%20the%20same%20constituency.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20formed%20its%20first%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%202014%2C%20Haribhau%20Bagde%20was%20appointed%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Assembly.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20Speaker%20in%20the%20state%20from%20BJP.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722162120000