ng%20its%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20his%20personal%20grievances%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bwoke%20mind%20virus%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20is%20still%20the%20CEO%20of%20Tesla%20and%20an%20electric-vehicle%20pioneer.%20On%20its%20face%2C%20a%20second%20Trump%20presidency%20would%20be%20bad%20for%20companies%20trying%20to%20move%20the%20country%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels.%20But%20on%20a%20Tuesday%20call%20with%20Tesla's%20investors%2C%20Musk's%20reasons%20for%20his%20support%20became%20crystal%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20worrying%20about%20society's%20move%20to%20an%20all-electric%20future%2C%20Musk%20is%20mainly%20concerned%20about%20maintaining%20Tesla's%20dominant%20position%20in%20the%20EV%20market.%20The%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%20one%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20defining%20legislative%20accomplishments%2C%20helped%20spur%20legacy%20carmakers%20to%20enter%20the%20EV%20game%20in%20earnest.%20As%20market%20competition%20heated%20up%2C%20Tesla%20started%20cutting%20prices%2C%20which%20turned%20into%20an%20industrywide%20price%20war%20that%20Tesla%20isn't%20winning.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Tesla's%20profits%20have%20fallen%20by%2045%25%2C%20and%20the%20company's%20market%20share%20has%20withered.%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book%20said%20that%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20overall%20EV%20sales%20in%20the%20US%20increased%2C%20but%20Tesla's%20share%20of%20those%20sales%20fell%20below%2050%25%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20company's%20history.%20It's%20a%20steep%20fall%2C%20considering%20Tesla's%20share%20of%20the%20EV%20market%20used%20to%20be%20as%20high%20as%2080%25.%20Without%20a%20new%20model%20to%20sell%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-recalls-cybertrucks-due-to-wiper-issue-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunless%20you%20count%20the%20Cybertruck%20for%20some%20reason%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20facing%20even%20more%20cutthroat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-xi-jinping-crush-tesla-elon-musk-american-ev-industry-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompetition%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tesla%20is%20under%20pressure%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20opened%20the%20company's%20investor%20call%20by%20saying%20the%20wave%20of%20competition%20killing%20its%20profits%20and%20shrinking%20its%20market%20share%20would%20pass%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20offer%20any%20reasoning.%20When%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20worried%20about%20Trump%20repealing%20the%20IRA%2C%20Musk%20tipped%20his%20hand.%20He%20told%20investors%20that%20the%20move%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%26quot%3B%20for%20Tesla's%20competitors%20but%20less%20so%20for%20Tesla%20%E2%80%94%20in%20fact%2C%20%26quot%3Blong%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20it%20would%20be%20good%20for%20Tesla.%20In%20essence%20this%20was%20an%20admission%20that%20Musk's%20best%20hope%20is%20that%20Trump%20returns%20to%20the%20White%20House%20and%20dismantles%20the%20regulatory%20regime%20that%20has%20encouraged%20legacy%20automakers%20to%20enter%20the%20EV%20market.%20The%20best%20thing%20for%20Tesla%20is%20if%20US%20legacy%20automakers%20like%20GM%20and%20Ford%20sit%20on%20the%20sidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20that%20while%20Musk%20may%20want%20the%20IRA%20gone%2C%20Tesla%20is%20still%20raking%20it%20in%20from%20government%20tax%20credits%20that%20predate%20the%20law.%20These%20are%20credits%20that%20EV%20makers%20can%20sell%20to%20combustion-engine%20carmakers%20to%20offset%20the%20latter's%20carbon%20emissions%20%E2%80%94%20the%20slower%20legacy%20automakers%20are%20to%20get%20into%20the%20EV%20game%2C%20the%20more%20Tesla%20can%20sell.%20And%20sell%20they%20are%3A%20Tesla%20made%20a%20life-saving%20%24890%20million%20in%20these%20credits%20last%20quarter%2C%20doubling%20its%20haul%20from%20the%20quarter%20before.%20Musk%20happily%20accepts%20government%20intervention%2C%20but%20only%20when%20it's%20for%20Tesla%20and%20not%20its%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20Trump%20have%20the%20same%20policy%20goal%20for%20EVs%3A%20to%20tear%20up%20Biden's%20EV%20regulatory%20infrastructure%20and%20revert%20to%20the%20old%20structure.%20Or%20maybe%20%E2%80%94%20if%20Musk's%20money%20gets%20some%20say%20in%20the%20White%20House%20%E2%80%94%20let%20him%20dream%20up%20some%20new%20rules%20that%20work%20for%20him.%20What%20it%20seems%20Musk%20and%20Trump%20most%20have%20in%20common%20is%20that%20they%20are%20both%20dedicated%20to%20law%20and%20order%20%E2%80%94%20so%20long%20as%20they%20write%20the%20laws%20and%20make%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20quarter%20of%20fantasy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20hard%20to%20see%20why%20Tesla%20is%20losing%20its%20dominant%20edge%3A%20The%20company%20is%20moving%20too%20slowly.%20Its%20last%20fresh%20model%2C%20the%20Model%20Y%2C%20came%20out%20in%202019.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20company%20has%20come%20under%20competitive%20pressure%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20In%20China%2C%20it's%20battling%20state-backed%20automakers%20that%20are%20producing%20state-of-the-art%20models%20for%20cheap.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20Legacy%20Auto%20is%20beginning%20to%20martial%20its%20forces%20to%20offer%20consumers%20more%20variety%20and%20%E2%80%94%20let's%20be%20real%20here%20%E2%80%94%20an%20alternative%20to%20Musk's%20cult%20of%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20maintain%20its%20market%20position%2C%20Tesla%20started%20slashing%20its%20prices%20in%202023.%20That%20kicked%20off%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-price-cuts-electric-cars-losing-business-strategy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20global%20EV%20price%20war%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Critics%20balked%2C%20but%20Musk%20assured%20the%20Tesla%20community%20that%20this%20was%20the%20only%20strategy%20to%20save%20the%20company.%20By%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-earnings-q3-report-live-updates-guidance-analyst-call-stock-reaction-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20third%20quarter%20of%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20price%20war%20had%20started%20ravaging%20Tesla's%20balance%20sheet.%20When%20it%20announced%20results%20in%20October%2C%20the%20company%20fell%20well%20short%20of%20expectations%20for%20revenue%2C%20vehicle%20deliveries%2C%20and%20free%20cash%20flow%2C%20which%20was%20down%20to%20%24848%20million%20from%20%243.4%20billion%20a%20year%20before.%20Gross%20margins%20%E2%80%94%20a%20measure%20of%20the%20company's%20profitability%20after%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20continued%20to%20shrink.%20For%20investors%2C%20this%20was%20a%20return%20to%20darker%20days%20at%20the%20company.%20Tesla%20turned%20its%20first%20annual%20profit%20in%202020%20and%20was%20purported%20to%20be%20on%20a%20stable%20path%20from%20that%20day%20forth.%20Its%20sudden%20financial%20backslide%20triggered%20Wall%20Street's%20PTSD%20%E2%80%94%20Tesla's%20stock%20fell%20by%20more%20than%2040%25%20over%20the%20following%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20stopped%20the%20bleeding%20in%20April%20by%20doing%20what%20he%20does%20best%3A%20talking%20up%20a%20world%20of%20fantastic%20innovations%20the%20company%20hasn't%20built%20yet.%20Tesla%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20not%20a%20car%20company%3B%20it%20is%20an%20AI%20company.%20He%20promised%20autonomous%20robotaxis%20by%20August%2C%20never%20mind%20that%20Musk%20has%20been%20promising%20the%20robotaxi%20for%20about%20a%20decade.%20He%20said%20the%20company%20was%20making%20headway%20with%20a%20new%20humanoid%20robot%20called%20Optimus%20%E2%80%94%20never%20mind%20that%20when%20Tesla%20unveiled%20Optimus%20it%20was%20a%20person%20dancing%20in%20a%20robot%20costume%2C%20and%20Tesla%20still%20won't%20say%20which%20tasks%20it%20can%20do.%20Musk%20glazed%20over%20the%20product%20the%20world%20really%20wants%20to%20see%2C%20a%20cheaper%20Tesla%20priced%20at%20about%20%2425%2C000%20to%20%2430%2C000.%20Without%20providing%20more%20detail%2C%20he%20mentioned%20that%20those%20models%20would%20start%20rolling%20out%20of%20factories%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025%2C%20never%20mind%20that%20Musk%20has%20been%20saying%20something%20like%20that%20since%202018.%20Musk%20threw%20out%20absolutely%20every%20trick%20he%20has%20ever%20trotted%20out%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20to%20regain%20Wall%20Street's%20confidence.%20And%20it%20worked.%20Despite%20warning%20signs%20about%20the%20company's%20ability%20to%20deliver%2C%20Wall%20Street%20seemed%20confident%20that%20Musk%20would%20pull%20off%20some%20miraculous%20turnaround.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fire-elon-musk-new-ceo-evs-china-sales-earnings-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20stock%20rallied%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20brings%20us%20to%20now%20and%20to%20Tesla's%20second-quarter%20earnings%20report.%20The%20results%20showed%20that%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20company%20or%20not%20%E2%80%94%20Tesla%20is%20still%20hurting%20because%20of%20new%20EV-market%20competition.%20The%20price%20war%20is%20still%20torching%20operating%20margins%2C%20which%20have%20slimmed%20to%206.3%25%20from%209.6%25%20a%20year%20ago.%20And%20automotive-sales%20revenue%20is%20down%207%25%20from%20this%20time%20last%20year%2C%20even%20as%20legacy%20automakers%20announced%20a%20slowdown%20in%20their%20rollout%20of%20EVs%20due%20to%20the%20price%20war%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20demand.%20That's%20why%2C%20in%20Musk's%20fantastic%20future%2C%20the%20IRA%20is%20repealed%20and%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%20for%20our%20competitors%20and%20for%20Tesla%20slightly%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20said.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20investors%20shouldn't%20even%20think%20about%20Tesla%20as%20a%20car%20company%20with%20car-company%20competitors%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20value%20of%20Tesla%20overwhelmingly%20is%20autonomy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20other%20things%20are%2C%20I%20think%2C%20no%20way%20it's%20relative%20to%