ld%2C%20it%20can%20buy%20ZEV%20credits%20from%20an%20automaker%20that%20makes%20cars%20with%20radically%20reduced%20emissions%2C%20like%20an%20EV%20maker.%20Since%20Tesla%20is%20a%20pure%20EV%20company%2C%20it%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20extra%20ZEV%20credits%20to%20sell%20off%20to%20companies%20still%20churning%20out%20gas-powered%20cars.%20This%20business%20is%20lucrative%20for%20Tesla%3A%20ZEV-credit%20sales%20made%20up%2068%25%20of%20the%20company's%20%241.3%20billion%20of%20free%20cash%20flow%20last%20quarter.%20Of%20course%2C%20if%20automakers%20sell%20their%20own%20EVs%2C%20offsetting%20their%20own%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20buy%20as%20many%20credits%20from%20Tesla.%20The%20tap%20of%20free%20money%20dries%20up%2C%20and%20Tesla%20has%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20sell%20more%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3c6e0a0fc5856d597bf0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222784%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMusk%20is%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20buy%20time%20for%20Tesla%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20of%20those%20ways%20is%20to%20get%20Trump%20elected.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Granitz%2FFilmMagic%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20hasn't%20said%20anything%20about%20ZEV%20credits.%20But%20the%20Heritage%20Foundation's%20Project%202025%20plan%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20a%20potential%20template%20for%20a%20second%20Trump%20administration%2C%20proposes%20eliminating%20government%20subsidies%20for%20EVs%20and%20lowering%20fuel-economy%20standards%20for%20combustion-engine%20cars.%20Musk%20probably%20figures%20the%20conservative%20super%20PAC%20to%20which%20he's%20contributing%20%2445%20million%20a%20month%20can%20take%20some%20of%20the%20edges%20off%20of%20that%20for%20Tesla%20while%20getting%20rid%20of%20the%20IRA%20incentives%20that%20are%20making%20life%20harder.%20On%20Tesla's%20quarter