%20career%20in%20the%20alternative%20asset%20management%20industry%20while%20pursuing%20her%20dreams%20on%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20from%20Harvard%20in%202011%2C%20Coffey%20was%20recruited%20by%20One%20Equity%20Partners%20in%20a%20back-office%20role.%20Her%20parents%20trained%20with%20the%20firm's%20founder%20Dick%20Cashin%20-%20he%20and%20her%20father%20Cal%20rowed%20for%20the%20US%20at%20the%201976%20Montreal%20Olympics%20(the%20elder%20Coffey%20won%20silver%20in%20the%20pair's%20event.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20her%20career%2C%20Coffey%20missed%20out%20on%20selection%20for%20the%20London%202012%20Olympics%20and%20was%20a%20spare%20for%20the%20Rio%202016%20Games.%20She%20worked%20on%20the%20firm's%20research%20and%20valuations%20team%20and%20rowed%20while%20obtaining%20her%20MBA%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20graduating%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20after%20winning%20the%20world%20championships%20in%20Plovdiv%2C%20Bulgaria%2C%20Coffey%20resumed%20work%20at%20One%20Equity%20Partners%20and%20targeted%20a%20place%20on%20the%20Olympic%20team%20-%20an%20effort%20that%20was%20rewarded%20with%20a%20berth%20in%20the%20women's%20eight%2C%20which%20placed%20fourth%20at%20the%20Covid-postponed%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Rowed%20to%20Paris'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20really%20awful%20feeling%20to%20walk%20away%20without%20getting%20to%20my%20ultimate%20goal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20ready%20to%20be%20done%20with%20rowing%2C%20but%20found%20my%20life%20wasn't%20balanced%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20something%20was%20missing%2C%26quot%3B%20Coffey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20resumed%20workouts%20in%20the%20office%20basement%20gym%2C%20attended%20CrossFit%20classes%20and%20began%20training%20with%20a%20group%20who%20communicated%20on%20an%20appropriately-named%20WhatsApp%20chat%3A%20'Rowed%20to%20Paris.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoffey%2C%20who%20lives%20between%20Princeton%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20Manhattan's%20Upper%20West%20Side%20and%20Watkins%20Glen%20in%20upstate%20New%20York%2C%20and%20spent%20the%20most%20recent%20winter%20in%20Sarasota%2C%20Florida%2C%20logs%2014%20to%2015%20exercise%20sessions%20per%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAwake%20at%205%3A30%20a.m.%20each%20morning%2C%20she%20spends%20about%20two%20hours%20on%20the%20water%20rowing%2020%20kilometres%20to%2030%20kilometres%2C%20and%20during%20afternoons%2C%20she%20spends%20about%2090%20minutes%20on%20another%20cardio%20or%20cross-training%20activity%2C%20be%20it%20running%20or%20cycling%20-%20sometimes%20in%20Central%20Park%20-%20or%20on%20the%20rowing%20machine%20or%20lifting%20weights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20usually%20hit%20250%20kilometres%20a%20week%2C%20or%2040%20kilometres%20to%2050%20kilometres%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Coffey%2C%20who%20rarely%20drinks%20alcohol%20when%20training.%20%26quot%3BI%20eat%20a%20ton%20of%20carbs%20-%20things%20like%20cookies%20and%20sweet%20drinks%2C%20which%20are%20not%20great%20for%20me%20long-term%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20not%20training%2C%20I'm%20recovering%20or%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20adds%20Coffey%2C%20who%20aims%20to%20be%20asleep%20by%2010%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20her%20work%20at%20One%20Equity%20Partners%2C%20Coffey%20sits%20on%20the%20board%20of%20Dragonfly%20Financial%20Technologies%2C%20a%20digital%20banking%20platform%2C%20and%20is%20a%20board%20observer%20for%20Montgomery%20Transport%2C%20a%20flatbed%20trucking%20operator%2C%20as%20well%20as%20staffing%20firm%20Prime%20Time%20Healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20Equity%20Partners'%20flexibility%20enabled%20Coffey%20to%20schedule%20work%20around%20her%20training.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20thankful%2C%20the%20firm%20couldn't%20have%20been%20more%20supportive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20really%20fortunate%20to%20have%20understanding%20deal%20teams%2C%20and%20colleagues%20who%20can%20accommodate%20my%20schedule.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20her%20rowing%20commitments%2C%20Coffey%20isn't%20subject%20to%20what%20she%20describes%20as%20a%20classic%2080-hour%20work%20week.%20%26quot%3BI%20work%20as%20much%20as%20I%20can%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Coffey%2C%20who%20generally%20logs%20on%20by%209.30%20a.m.%20or%2010%20a.m.%20each%20morning.%20Through%20the%20fall%2C%20when%20she%20was%20training%20intensely%20ahead%20of%20team%20trials%20in%20March%2C%20she%20notched%20an%20average%20work%20week%20of%2040%20hours.%20In%20the%20lead-up%20to%20Paris%2C%20that%20number%20has%20halved%20to%20about%2020%20hours%2C%20as%20she%20focuses%20on%20portfolio%20management%20and%20opts%20out%20of%20originating%20new%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOlympians%20Everywhere%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0US%20Olympic%20Committee%C2%A0gives%20rowers%20a%20stipend%20of%20%241%2C000%20to%20%242%2C000%20a%20month%20in%20addition%20to%20health%20insurance%2C%20which%20a%20lot%20of%20athletes%20supplement%20with%20full-time%20work%2C%20said%20Coffey%2C%20who%20on%20a%20regular%20day%2C%20can%20jump%20from%20working%20on%20a%20financial%20model%20in%20Microsoft%20Excel%20to%20a%20board%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20role%2C%20she%20deals%20with%20everything%20from%20origination%20to%20due%20diligence%20to%20hashing%20out%20terms%20of%20a%20credit%20agreement%2C%20and%20she%20especially%20enjoys%20meeting%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20be%20super%20passionate%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20sacrifice%20and%20perseverance%20it%20takes%20to%20put%20everything%20you%20have%20into%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Coffey%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20love%20what%20they%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe'll%20be%20supported%20in%20Paris%20by%20her%20family%20including%20husband%20Michael%20Blomquist%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20renewable%20energy%20project%20finance%20brokerage%20Open%20Energy%20Group%2C%20who%20has%20made%20blue%20tops%20emblazoned%20with%20%26quot%3BGo%20Liv!%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20cheer%20squad.%20Blomquist%20understands%20Coffey's%20drive%20all%20too%20well%20-%20he%20quit%20Morgan%20Stanley%20to%20focus%20on%20qualifying%20for%20a%20spot%20on%20the%20London%202012%20US%20Olympic%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20there%20will%20be%20Jamie%20Koven%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20One%20Equity%20Partners%2C%20a%20co-chair%20of%20the%20National%20Rowing%20Foundation%20and%20former%20Olympic%20rower%20himself%2C%20having%20competed%20at%20the%20Olympics%20in%201996%20and%202000%20in%20Atlanta%20and%20Sydney%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoven%20and%20Cashin%20are%20not%20the%20only%20co-workers%20to%20have%20competed%20at%20the%20Olympics.%20Senior%20adviser%20Fritz%20Hobbs%2C%20partners%20Charlie%20Cole%2C%20Matthew%20Hughes%2C%20Ante%20Kusurin%2C%20and%20associate%20Jack%20Lopas%2C%20all%20rowed%20at%20prior%20Summer%20Olympics%2C%20and%20principal%20Mario%20Ancic%20is%20a%20former%20professional%20tennis%20player%20who%20won%20a%20bronze%20medal%20at%20the%20Athens%202004%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722158460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fqc9adf2g_olivia-coffey_625x300_28_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeet-olivia-coffey-a-private-equity-staffer-eyeing-gold-at-olympics-6207001%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Private%20equity%20staffers%20regularly%20frequent%20the%20basement%20gym%20at%20510%20Madison%20Avenue%20in%20Manhattan.%20Among%20them%3A%20an%20athlete%20preparing%20to%20don%20the%20red%2C%20white%20and%20blue%20in%20her%20second%20Summer%20Olympi