ir%20scientific%20work%20and%20are%20safe%2C%20says%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20update%2C%20the%20American%20space%20agency%20officials%20today%20said%20they%20conducted%20a%20'hot%20test'%20on%20the%20troubled%20spacecraft%2C%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%2C%20where%20the%20malfunctioning%20thrusters%20or%20rockets%20were%20tested%20while%20still%20being%20docked%20to%20the%20space%20station.%20%26quot%3BThe%20thrusters%20performed%20at%20peak%20thrust%20rating%20values%20and%20the%20helium%20system%20remained%20stable.%26quot%3B%20The%20world%20hopes%20that%20the%20Starliner%20could%20well%20return%20safely%20and%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20her%20crewmate%20Butch%20Wilmore%20reached%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20on%20June%206%20on%20a%2010-day%20mission%2C%20but%20have%20been%20stuck%20after%20the%20Starliner%20malfunctioned.%20They%20do%20not%20know%20when%20and%20how%20they%20will%20return%20to%20Earth%2C%20though%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20asserts%20she%20and%20the%20eight%20other%20astronauts%20on-board%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20are%20safe%20and%20in%20%26quot%3Bgood%20spirits%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20video%2C%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20her%20fellow%20astronauts%20are%20seen%20playing%20sports%20in%20the%20weightless%20atmosphere%20to%20send%20good%20wishes%20to%20the%20athletes%20participating%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2059-year-old%20Navy%20test%20pilot%20looks%20fit%20and%20in%20great%20spirits.%20She%20has%20helped%20design%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20and%20flew%20as%20its%20pilot%20on%20the%20maiden%20crewed%20test%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20has%20suggested%20that%20they%20are%20close%20to%20understanding%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20what%20is%20wrong%20with%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner's%20malfunctioning%20systems%2C%20but%20has%20given%20no%20clarity%20on%20when%20Williams%20and%20her%20crew%20mate%20Butch%20Wilmore%20will%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Boeing%2C%20the%20Starliner%20can%20remain%20docked%20with%20the%20space%20station%20for%20a%20maximum%20period%20of%20ninety%20days%2C%20after%20which%20the%20batteries%20on%20board%20this%20spacecraft%20may%20drain%20out.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20space%20technologists%20in%20the%20US%20have%20less%20than%20six%20weeks%20to%20determine%20if%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20will%20return%20on%20the%20handicapped%20Boeing%20Starliner%20spacecraft%20or%20on%20SpaceX's%20Crew%20Dragon%20or%20Russian%20Soyuz%20spacecraft.%20These%20standby%20vehicles%20are%20already%20docked%20to%20the%20space%20station%2C%20so%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20the%20other%20eight%20astronauts%20are%20not%20really%20stranded%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20faced%20several%20hiccups%20in%20the%20Starliner%20development.%20Initially%2C%20it%20was%20to%20have%20completed%20this%20with%20a%20%244.2%20billion%20contract%20but%20has%20now%20spent%20a%20total%20of%20about%20%245.7%20billion%20and%20the%20going%20is%20still%20uphill%20as%20the%20mission%20remains%20incomplete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20wanted%20an%20alternative%20to%20SpaceX's%20Crew%20Dragon%2C%20and%20hence%20Boeing%20Starliner%20was%20being%20pushed%20through.%20Boeing%20is%20also%20going%20through%20a%20bad%20patch%20in%20general%2C%20and%20its%20aviation%20and%20aircraft%20business%20has%20also%20been%20stumbling.%20Recently%2C%20Boeing%20CEO%20David%20Calhoun%20was%20grilled%20by%20US%20Senators%20regarding%20the%20aviation%20giant's%20safety%20culture%20and%20transparency.%20If%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20fails%20to%20bring%20the%20two%20astronauts%20back%20to%20Earth%2C%20it%20would%20leave%20the%20aviation%20and%20space%20tech%20giant%20red-faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20today's%20hot%20test%2C%20whose%20results%20are%20still%20being%20assessed%20by%20Boeing%20and%20NASA%2C%20there%20is%20hope%20that%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20could%20return%20to%20Earth%20before%20the%20latest%20crew%20of%20four%20astronauts%20heads%20to%20the%20space%20station.%20The%20new%20crew%20will%20be%20onboard%20SpaceX's%20Falcon-9%20rocket%20and%20Crew%20Dragon%20and%20the%20lift-off%20is%20likely%20after%20August%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722157620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fdimhhbao_international-space-station_625x300_28_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fsunita-williams-paris-olympics-how-sunita-williams-stuck-in-space-wished-all-the-best-to-paris-olympians-6206874%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%2052%20days%20and%20counting%2C%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20is%20in%20limbo%20at%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20but%20in%20a%20new%20video%2C%20she%20is%20seen%20celebrating%20the%20Olympics%20spirit%20in%20the%20weightless%20atmosphere%2C%20400%20kilometres%20above%20Paris.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fsunita-williams-paris-olympics-how-sunita-williams-stuck-in-space-wished-all-the-best-to-paris-olympians-6206874%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fsunita-williams-paris-olympics-how-sunita-williams-stuck-in-space-wished-all-the-best-to-paris-olympians-6206874%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fsunita-williams-paris-olympics-how-sunita-williams-stuck-in-space-wished-all-the-best-to-paris-olympians-6206874%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Seungkwan%20saved%20a%20friend%20from%20bullying%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722156661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112080351%2Cimgsize-38342.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fseventeens-seungkwans-