C%20while%20Google%20Maps%20introduced%20AI-driven%20features%20to%20improve%20navigation.%20CrowdStrike's%20explains%20how%20its%20faulty%20update%20caused%20a%20global%20IT%20disruption.%20Jio%20launched%20a%20feature%20phone%20and%20a%20new%204G%20device%20for%20two-wheelers.%20Other%20significant%20tech%20releases%20included%20HP's%20AI%20PCs%2C%20Asus's%20All-in-One%20PC%2C%20and%20HMD's%20Crest%20smartphones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fapple-iphone-price-cut-google-maps-new-features-microsoft-outage-update-and-other-top-tech-news-of-the-week%2Farticleshow%2F112079387.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Astrologer%20Who%20Correctly%20Predicted%20Biden%20Exit%2C%20Now%20'Names'%20Next%20US%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20astrologer%20who%20correctly%20predicted%20the%20day%20Joe%20Biden%20would%20end%20his%20re-election%20campaign%20now%20has%20predicted%20who%20will%20be%20the%20next%20United%20States%20President.%20Dubbed%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Binternet's%20most%20notorious%20astrologer%26quot%3B%2C%20Amy%20Tripp%20said%20according%20to%20the%20stars%2C%20the%20next%20President%20could%20be%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F07%2F27%2Fus-news%2Finternets-most-notorious-astrologer-who-predicted-bidens-exit-reveals-next-president%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Trump%20is%20enjoying%20the%20height%20of%20his%20professional%20success.%20Ms%20Tripp%20argues%20that%20the%20former%20President%C2%A0might%20be%20in%20for%20more%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%20things%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20considering%20that%20he%20was%20already%20the%20target%20of%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20this%20month.%20%26quot%3BUranus%20is%20on%20his%20mid-heaven%20which%20shows%20...%20unpredictability%20with%20his%20career%20and%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040-year-old%20astrologer%20went%20viral%20for%20accurately%20predicting%20when%20the%2081-year-old%20Joe%20Biden%20would%20abandon%20his%20presidential%20ambitions.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Biden%20is%20made%20to%20step%20down%20it%20will%20be%20at%20the%20Capricorn%20Full%20Moon%20at%2029%20degrees%20Capricorn.%20Capricorn%20rules%20the%20government%20and%20old%20age.%2029%20degrees%20is%20an%20ending%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20July%2011.%20When%20an%20X%20user%20questioned%20her%20about%20the%20precise%20date%2C%20she%20replied%20%26quot%3BJuly%2021.%26quot%3B%20The%20woman%20predicted%20Mr%20Biden's%20departure%20since%20it%20was%20a%20full%20moon%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Tripp%20also%20foretold%20that%20Kamala%20Harris%20would%20run%20for%20US%20President%20in%202024.%20Citing%20the%20reason%2C%20she%20said%2C%20Mr%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bis%20too%20old.%26quot%3B%20She%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20she%20felt%20the%20Vice%20President%20would%20win%20the%20nomination%20since%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bexperiencing%20her%20second%20Saturn%20return.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20time%20when%20if%20you've%20been%20putting%20in%20the%20work%20since%20the%20first%20Saturn%20return%20at%2030%20you're%20rewarded%20...%20usually%20there's%20a%20(professional)%20advancement%20or%20you%20gain%20authority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20astrologer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20she%20added%20that%20Mr%20Biden%20could%20experience%20more%20difficulties%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20%26quot%3BPluto%20is%20on%20his%20sun.%20He%20could%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20health%20crisis%20come%20up%20or%20his%20health%20could%20continue%20to%20decline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Tripp%20also%20predicted%20that%20the%20month%20of%20August%20in%20the%20US%20may%20be%20difficult%20and%20that%20there%