0ceremony%20began%20with%20a%20performance%20by%20Lady%20Gaga%20and%20included%20a%20tribute%20to%20French%20culture%2C%20history%20and%20sport.%20Athletes%20from%20205%20National%20Olympic%20Committees%20(NOC)%20participated%20in%20the%20parade%2C%20which%20travelled%20along%20the%20Seine%20and%20passed%20by%20iconic%20landmarks%20such%20as%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower%2C%20Notre-Dame%20and%20the%20Grand%20Palais.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Zidane%2C%20the%20Olympic%20torch%20was%20also%20carried%20by%20French%20sporting%20heroes%20Teddy%20Riner%20and%20Marie-Jose%20Perec%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Spanish%20Tennis%20legend%20Rafael%20Nadal.%20The%20cauldron%2C%20attached%20to%20a%20hot%20air%20balloon%2C%20rose%20into%20the%20sky%20as%20Celine%20Dion%20performed%20%3Cem%3EL'hymne%20%C3%A0%20l'amour%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower%20balcony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20was%20attended%20by%20320%2C000%20spectators%20along%20the%20Seine%20and%20watched%20by%20millions%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722144480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fdi7t5qp_masked-torchbearer-getty_625x300_28_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-was-the-masked-torchbearer-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-6205762%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Paris%20Olympics%20ceremony%20saw%20two%20unique%20figures%20-%20a%20masked%20torchbearer%20running%20across%20rooftops%20and%20a%20caped%20rider%20who%20rode%20a%20metal%20horse%20down%20the%20Seine%2C%20delivering%20the%20Olympic%20flag.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-was-the-masked-torchbearer-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-6205762%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-was-the-masked-torchbearer-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-6205762%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22a