r%20talks%20between%20U.S.%20authorities%20and%20El%20Chapo's%20son%2C%20Joaquin%20Guzman%20Lopez%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20But%20many%20American%20officials%20had%20given%20up%20hope%20on%20Joaquin%20turning%20himself%20in%2C%20and%20were%20caught%20unaware%20when%20he%20sent%20a%20last-minute%20message%20that%20he%20would%20arrive%20with%20a%20kingpin%20U.S.%20authorities%20had%20been%20chasing%20for%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEl%20Mayo%20was%20the%20cherry%20on%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20U.S.%20official%2C%20who%20declined%20to%20be%20identified%20because%20he%20was%20not%20authorized%20to%20speak%20publicly%20about%20the%20arrests.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20expected%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuzman%20Lopez%20had%20convinced%20Zambada%20to%20board%20the%20plane%20by%20telling%20him%20that%20they%20were%20flying%20to%20see%20real%20estate%20in%20northern%20Mexico%2C%20according%20to%20the%20two%20current%20and%20one%20former%20U.S.%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20was%20the%20first%20news%20organization%20to%20report%20the%20arrests%2C%20ahead%20of%20a%20Department%20of%20Justice%20statement%20on%20Thursday%20evening%20that%20confirmed%20the%20two%20men%20had%20been%20detained%20in%20El%20Paso.%20The%20news%20agency%20spoke%20to%20current%20and%20former%20officials%20to%20piece%20together%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI)%20and%20the%20Homeland%20Security%20Investigations%20(HSI)%2C%20the%20two%20agencies%20who%20carried%20out%20the%20operation%2C%20scrambled%20agents%20from%20their%20local%20El%20Paso%20offices%20and%20barely%20reached%20the%20airport%20by%20the%20time%20the%20private%20plane%20was%20landing%2C%20according%20to%20a%20fifth%20source%2C%20a%20U.S.%20official%20who%20declined%20to%20give%20further%20details%20on%20the%20arrests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20worker%20at%20the%20Dona%20Ana%20County%20International%20Jetport%2C%20near%20El%20Paso%2C%20told%20Reuters%20he%20saw%20a%20Beechcraft%20King%20Air%20plane%20land%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%20on%20the%20runway%2C%20where%20federal%20agents%20were%20already%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20individuals%20got%20off%20the%20plane%20...%20and%20were%20calmly%20taken%20into%20custody%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20man%2C%20who%20declined%20to%20share%20his%20name%20out%20of%20concern%20for%20his%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unexpected%20arrest%20of%20El%20Mayo%2C%20in%20his%20late%2070s%2C%20and%20the%20way%20he%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20betrayed%20by%20Guzman%20Lopez%2C%20who%20is%20about%2038%20years%20old%2C%20has%20jolted%20the%20Mexican%20drug%20trafficking%20world%2C%20triggering%20fears%20of%20a%20bloody%20fissure%20in%20the%20Sinaloa%20Cartel%20between%20the%20two%20families%20that%20control%20the%20group's%20biggest%20power%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZambada%20is%20accused%20of%20being%20one%20of%20the%20most%20consequential%20traffickers%20in%20Mexico's%20history%2C%20having%20co-founded%20the%20Sinaloa%20Cartel%20with%20%26quot%3BEl%20Chapo%26quot%3B%20Guzman%2C%20who%20was%20extradited%20to%20the%20U.S.%20in%202017%20and%20is%20serving%20a%20life%20sentence%20in%20a%20maximum%20security%20prison%20in%20Colorado.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20could%20not%20determine%20why%20Guzman%20Lopez%20betrayed%20his%20father's%20long-time%20partner%2C%20though%20the%20four%20current%20and%20former%20sources%20said%20it%20was%20likely%20due%20to%20his%20desire%20to%20obtain%20a%20more%20favourable%20plea%20bargain%20deal%20from%20U.S.%20authorities%20and%20help%20his%20brother%2C%20Ovidio%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20and%20extradited%20to%20the%20United%20States%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20authorities%20have%20made%20drug%20bosses%20key%20targets%2C%20frequently%20striking%20plea%20bargain%20deals%20with%20them%20in%20exchange%20for%20information%20that%20leads%20to%20the%20capture%20of%20other%20high-ranking%20cartel%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20back-channel%20communication%20between%20American%20officials%20and%20Guzman%20Lopez%20was%20carried%20out%20through%20lawyers%2C%20the%20first%20official%20said.%20Jeffrey%20Lichtman%2C%20who%20represents%20both%20Guzman%20brothers%2C%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZambada%2C%20who%20was%20in%20a%20wheelchair%2C%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20on%20Friday%20in%20a%20Texas%20courtroom%20to%20drug%20charges%2C%20including%20continuing%20criminal%20enterprise%2C%20narcotics%20importation%20conspiracy%20and%20money%20laundering.%20His%20lawyer%2C%20Frank%20Perez%2C%20said%20Zambada%20did%20not%20come%20to%20the%20U.S.%20voluntarily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuzman%20Lopez%20is%20due%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20next%20week%20in%20Chicago%2C%20where%20he%20was%20first%20indicted%20on%20drugs%20charges%20around%206%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuzman%20Lopez%20is%20one%20of%20four%20sons%20of%20El%20Chapo%20-%20known%20as%20Los%20Chapitos%2C%20or%20Little%20Chapos%20-%20who%20inherited%20their%20father's%20faction%20of%20the%20cartel.%20Joaquin%20and%20Ovidio%20have%20the%20same%20mother%2C%20while%20the%20other%20two%20siblings%20-%20Ivan%20and%20Jesus%20Alfredo%20-%20hail%20from%20El%20Chapo's%20first%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20have%20in%20recent%20years%20come%20under%20ferocious%20pressure%20from%20U.S.%20authorities%2C%20who%20have%20made%20them%20their%20main%20anti-narcotics%20targets%2C%20portraying%20them%20and%20the%20Sinaloa%20Cartel%20as%20the%20biggest%20traffickers%20of%20fentanyl%20into%20the%20United%20States.%20Fentanyl%20overdoses%20have%20surged%20to%20become%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20for%20Americans%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2045.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERay%20Donovan%2C%20a%20former%20high-ranking%20U.S.%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Administration%20(DEA)%20official%2C%20said%20the%20defeats%20suffered%20by%20key%20Sinaloa%20Cartel%20bosses%20in%20recent%20past%20are%20mainly%20down%20to%20their%20embrace%20of%20fentanyl%2C%20which%20has%20risen%20up%20the%20political%20agenda%20in%20Washington%20as%20the%20death%20told%20has%20mounted%20on%20U.S.%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20Americans%20dying%20has%20put%20a%20lot%20more%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20Donovan%20said.%20%26quot%3BFentanyl%20brought%20them%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20heralded%20the%20arrests%20and%20vowed%20to%20continue%20combating%20%26quot%3Bthe%20scourge%20of%20fentanyl%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Generation%20Of%20Narcos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEl%20Chapo's%20sons%20are%20known%20to%20be%20more%20violent%20and%20hot-headed%20than%20Zambada%2C%20who%20had%20a%20reputation%20as%20a%20shrewd%20operator%20that%20liked%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20shadows.%20Guzman%20Lopez%20was%20also%20seen%20as%20less%20important%20than%20his%20other%20three%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20authorities%20had%20a%20%2415%20million%20reward%20for%20the%20capture%20of%20Zambada%2C%20who%20co-founded%20the%20Sinaloa%20Cartel%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20with%20El%20Chapo.%20Guzman%20Lopez%20had%20a%20%245%20million%20bounty%20on%20his%20head.%20Both%20men%20face%20multiple%20indictments%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20U.S.%20official%20cautioned%20that%20there%20are%20still%20many%20questions%20unanswered%20about%20how%20or%20why%20Zambada%2C%20an%20ultra-cautious%20and%20experienced%20cartel%20chieftain%2C%20found%20himself%20on%20that%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexican%20Security%20Minister%20Rosa%20Rodriguez%20said%20that%20Mexico%20was%20informed%20of%20the%20detentions%20by%20the%20U.S.%20government%2C%20but%20that%20Mexican%20authorities%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutgoing%20Mexican%20President%20Andres%20Manuel%20Lopez%20Obrador%20has%20taken%20a%20cautious%20approach%20to%20tackling%20the%20powerful%20cartels%2C%20curbing%20security%20cooperation%20with%20U.S.%20authorities%20on%20fears%20that%20the%20previous%20U.S.-Mexico%20strategy%20of%20targeting%20powerful%20kingpins%20was%20triggering%20more%20nationwide%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Oct.%202019%2C%20Mexico's%20military%20arrested%20Ovidio%20but%20were%20forced%20to%20release%20him%20after%20hundreds%20of%20Sinaloa%20Cartel%20foot%20soldiers%20blocked%20roads%20and%20fought%20running%20gun%20battles%20with%20soldiers%20as%20they%20to%20lay%20siege%20to%20the%20city%20of%20Culiacan%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Sinaloa.%20The%20military%20arrested%20Ovidio%20again%20in%20Jan.%202023%20and%20he%20was%20extradited%20in%20September%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Allen%2C%20a%20former%20Special%20Agent%20in%20Charge%20of%20HSI's%20Arizona%20division%20that%20built%20indictments%20against%20Guzman%20Lopez%20and%20other%20Sinaloa%20Cartel%20figures%2C%20said%20both%20Zambada%20and%20Guzman%20Lopez%20had%20had%20periodic%20conversations%20with%20U.S.%20officials%20about%20surrendering%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllen%2C%20who%20maintains%20regular%20contact%20with%20former%20colleagues%20at%20HSI%2C%20said%20many%20traffickers%2C%20especially%20those%20from%20the%20younger%20generation%2C%20realize%20that%20giving%20themselves%20up%2C%20serving%20some%20time%20in%20jail%20and%20then%20spending%20their%20wealth%20is%20a%20better%20option%20than%20risking%20death%20from%20rivals%20in%20Mexico%20or%20capture%20by%20authorities%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20lifelong%20prison%20terms.%20Some%20informants%20are%20allowed%20to%20enter%20witness%20protection%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20seeing%20that%20this%20way%20you%20can%20do%20your%20time%20and%20do%20not%20have%20to%20look%20over%20your%20shoulder%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20f