n.%20As%20Kabi%20probed%20further%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20many%20villages%20along%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20coastline%20were%20victims%20of%20a%20similar%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20worse%20%E2%80%94%20fate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20help%2C%20Kabi%20noted%20that%20geosynthetic%20tubes%20were%20installed%20to%20prevent%20soil%20erosion%20along%20the%20boundaries.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20even%20this%20could%20not%20stop%20the%20calamity.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20now%2015%20years%20since%20he%20decided%20to%20devote%20his%20time%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250802%2Fodisha-mangrove-planting-save-forest-village-cyclone-stop-how-bijay-kumar-kabi-environment-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emangrove%20conservation%20and%20planting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20restored%20mangroves%20on%2014%20acres%20at%20Jagannathpur%20village%2C%2015%20acres%20at%20Padmanavpur%2C%2025%20acres%20in%20Badkot%2C%2010%20acres%20at%20Dibakarpur%20in%20Kendrapada%20district%2C%20and%2010%20acres%20at%20Kankana%20village%20in%20Jagatsinghpur%20district%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Kandal%20Rajan%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kandal%20Rajan%20has%20planted%20mangroves%20along%20the%20Pazhayangadi%20River%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuplo